  <context>
    <background>
      Task 062's report identified the 8 sibling fixtures and their associated failure counts:

      | Fixture | Failures |
      |---|---:|
      | SemanticSearchTestFixture | 22 |
      | SemanticSearchAuthorizationTestFixture | 14 |
      | RecordSearchTestFixture | 13 |
      | KnowledgeBaseTestFixture | 13 |
      | AnalysisTestFixture | 12 |
      | ChatEndpointsTestFixture | 11 |
      | ReAnalysisFlowTestFixture | 8 |
      | AuthorizationTestFixture | 5 |
      | **TOTAL** | **98** |

      Pattern recognition: tasks 018 (CustomWebAppFactory.cs), 060 (WorkspaceTestFixture.cs),
      and 062 (IntegrationTestFixture.cs) all applied the SAME fix — extend the test-side
      config dictionary with the keys that production demands at startup. The 8 sibling
      fixtures need either (a) the same dict entries copied in, or (b) refactored to
      inherit `IntegrationTestFixture` (which already has them).

      Prefer (b) inheritance when possible — DRY, less drift, single source of truth.
      Fall back to (a) duplication if inheritance would break test isolation, parallelism,
      or other fixture-specific needs (likely fine since the keys are pure config values
      with no side effects).

      Locate the 8 fixtures (likely under `tests/integration/Spe.Integration.Tests/`
      or its `Fixtures/` subdirectory). Use Glob.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
