    <criterion testable="true">No modifications to `IntegrationTestFixture.cs` (sealed by task 062) or `CustomWebAppFactory.cs` (sealed by task 018)</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    <completion-notes date="2026-05-31">
      Executed 2026-05-31 (FULL rigor). Delta: 108 → 47 Failed (−61, −56.5%). Cluster B
      (98 SpeAdmin/Cosmos config failures) fully cleared — `grep 'KeyVaultUri is not configured'`
      returns 0 in post-027 TRX (was 196 mentions in post-062).

      Decision: COPY (additive) over inheritance. Each sibling has substantial custom logic
      (auth handlers, conditional stubs, feature flags) that inheriting `IntegrationTestFixture`
      would break. NFR-02 strongly favors minimal additive 2-LOC fixes (≤8.5% diff per file).

      6 files modified (8 fixtures — 3 share `SemanticSearch/TestHostConfiguration.cs`):
        1. SemanticSearch/TestHostConfiguration.cs (+10 lines)  — fixes Semantic+SemanticAuth+RecordSearch fixtures
        2. AnalysisEndpointsIntegrationTests.cs (+11 lines)     — AnalysisTestFixture
        3. AuthorizationIntegrationTests.cs (+11 lines)         — AuthorizationTestFixture
        4. Api/Ai/KnowledgeBaseEndpointsTests.cs (+11 lines)    — KnowledgeBaseTestFixture
        5. Api/Ai/ReAnalysisFlowTests.cs (+11 lines)            — ReAnalysisFlowTestFixture
        6. Api/Ai/ChatEndpointsTests.cs (+11 lines)             — ChatEndpointsTestFixture

      Residual 37 sibling-cluster Failed are NOT config — they're param-inference / Moq /
      assertion-level issues SURFACED now that host boots cleanly (was previously masked by
      `KeyVaultUri is not configured` startup throw). Same anti-drift pattern as `Analysis:Enabled=false`
      + new services in Program.cs over time. These are Wave 2.5 / P23.L follow-up scope, not this
      task's. §6.2 trait-tagging DEFERRED to follow-up.

      0 §4.8 escalations. 0 real-bug ledger entries. 0 production-code changes. §4.5 honored
      (CustomWebAppFactory.cs + IntegrationTestFixture.cs untouched).

      Reference: `baseline/post-027-delta-2026-05-31.md` (full per-file table + residual triage).
    </completion-notes>
